<text top="941" left="76" width="794" height="11" font="8"><b>On the above date and time I was dispatched to McDonalds at 2211 S Sterling St. While I was on the</b></text>
<text top="956" left="76" width="753" height="11" font="8"><b>way to the call dispatch advised that the suspect was yelling and attempting to go behind the</b></text>
<text top="971" left="76" width="769" height="11" font="8"><b>counter. When I arrived I observed a older white male talking on the phone near the front door.</b></text>
<text top="987" left="76" width="794" height="11" font="8"><b>He matched the description of the suspect but was talking on the phone. I walked past the male who</b></text>
<text top="1002" left="76" width="769" height="11" font="8"><b>I later identified as Christian Rider and walked inside the store. I spoke with an employee who</b></text>
